org.json.stream

Class CollectionCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.json.stream.CollectionCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StructureCollector<java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>,java.util.List<java.lang.Object>,java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>,java.util.List<java.lang.Object>>

    public final class CollectionCollector
extends java.lang.Object
implements StructureCollector<java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>,java.util.List<java.lang.Object>,java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>,java.util.List<java.lang.Object>>
    Structure collector that creates HashMap, ArrayList, and null instances. The result types are finished using Collections.unmodifiableMap() and Collections.unmodifiableList().

    This collector holds no state, so a singleton is provided.
